object.script:
s,i,o,m=self,input,output,math pgn,pgb,gn,gb,sn,sb=property.getNumber,property.getBool,i.getNumber,i.getBool,o.setNumber,o.setBool abs=m.abs t,f=true,false
function clamp(x,min,max) return m.max(m.min(x,max),min) end function sgn(x) return (x>=0 and 1) or -1 end function lerp(min,max,t) local t=clamp(t,0,1) return min*(1-t)+max*t end function pid(p,i) return{p=p,i=i,err=0,integral=0, run=function(s,sp,pv,min,max,maxI,reset) local reset=reset or f local maxI=maxI or max local err,out err=sp-pv diff=err-s.err s.err=err out=err*s.p+s.integral if reset then s.integral=0 elseif out>min and out<max then s.integral=clamp(s.integral+err*s.i,min,maxI) end return clamp(err*s.p+s.integral,min,max) end}end
rpsMin=m.max(pgn("Idle RPS"),3) rpsMax=m.max(pgn("Full throttle RPS"),rpsMin) boostMax=0.1*pgn("Reduce if RPS overshoots") thrRev=pgn("Reverse max throttle") afr=pgn("Air-to-Fuel ratio") brSens=pgn("Brakes sensitivity") prot=pgn("Overheat protection") type=pgn("Transmission type") topMax=pgn("Top gear") mode=pgb("Default mode") and 0 or 1 delay=not pgb("Gear shift delay") auto=not pgb("Autostart if engine stalls") ratios={} mean,tick,tickMax=0,1,10 sens,wsR=1,1 wsS,wsB,t1,t2,t3,rpsOld,wsOld=0,0,0,0,0,0,0 grC=mode+2 gr=grC rpsS=pgn("Shift RPS") rev,heat,starter,stall,init=f,f,f,f,f
for i=1,tickMax do ratios[i]=0 end
grs={{-1,f,f,t}, {-1,f,f,f}, {0.16,f,f,f}, {0.22,f,t,f}, {0.31,f,f,t}, {0.4,f,t,t}, {0.5,t,f,f}, {0.68,t,t,f}, {0.9,t,f,t}, {1.21,t,t,t}}
pidAfr=pid(0.01,0.002) pidEngine=pid(0.15,0.002)
function onTick() air=gn(1) fuel=gn(2) temp=gn(3) rps=gn(4) rpsW=gn(5) ws=gn(6)
onP=gb(1) and not on on=gb(1) upP=gb(2) and not up up=gb(2) downP=gb(3) and not down down=gb(3) parkbreak= not gb(4) lowgear=gb(5) if not init and ws~=0 then sens=m.max(abs(ws-wsOld),0.001) init=t end init=sens>0.001 if parkbreak then mode=0 else if lowgear and (mode<1 or mode==2 or rpsW<rpsS*grs[3][1]) then mode=2 else mode=1 end end
if abs(rpsW)<0.2 and ws>0.01 then wsR=1 elseif abs(rpsW)<0.2 and ws<-0.01 then wsR=-1 end
top=mode==2 and 3 or topMax if mode==0 then gr,grC=2,2 elseif mode==-1 or wsR==-1 then gr,grC=1,1 elseif rpsW>rpsS*grs[top][1] then gr=top elseif grC==gr then for i=3,top do if rpsW>rpsS*grs[i-1][1] and rpsW<=rpsS*grs[i][1] then t3=m.min(t3+1,30) if not delay or grC==2 or t3>=30 then t3,gr=0,i break end end end end
if delay and gr~=grC then wsR=0 if wsS<0.5 then grC=gr wsR=1 end else grC=gr end
rev=grC==1 park=grC==2 gb1,gb2,gb3,gb4=grs[grC][2],grs[grC][3],grs[grC][4],grC==1
wsS=wsS+clamp(wsR*ws-wsS,-sens,sens) wsT=m.max(wsS,0) wsB=m.max(wsB-(ws+wsOld*(sens-1))*wsR-wsB*sens,0) throttle=rev and wsT*thrRev or wsT
clutch=park and 0 or wsT*lerp(0.3,0.8,abs(rpsW)/(rpsMax*grs[3][1])) brakes=park and 1 or wsB*0.2*clamp(brSens/(abs(rpsW)*2.5+brSens*0.5),0,1) rpsSp=lerp(rpsMin,rpsMax,throttle)
if prot==0 then rpsSp=lerp(lerp(rpsMin,rpsMax,throttle),3,(temp-100)/10) elseif prot==1 then if temp>110 then heat=t elseif temp<100 then heat=f end end
if not heat and on and rps>=2 then if fuel>0 then ratios[tick]=air/fuel else ratios[tick]=0 end tick=tick+1 if tick>tickMax then tick=1 end mean=0 for i,ratio in ipairs(ratios) do mean=mean+ratio end mean=mean/tickMax if mean>0 then boost=pidAfr:run(afr,mean,-0.52,0.2) else boost=pidAfr:run(0,0,0,0,0,t) end airMan=pidEngine:run(rpsSp,rps,0.01,1,boostMax) fuelMan=airMan*(0.48-boost) else airMan=0 fuelMan=0 pidEngine:run(0,0,0,0,0,t) pidAfr:run(0,0,0,0,0,t) tick=1 end
if rpsOld>=2 and rps<2 then stall=t end if auto or onP then stall=f end if rps>=2 then t1,t2=0,m.min(t2+1,30) else t1,t2=m.min(t1+1,60),0 end if on and not stall and t2<30 and t1>=60 and not heat then starter=t elseif not on or heat or t2>=30 then starter=f end rpsOld,wsOld=rps,ws
sn(1,airMan) sn(2,fuelMan) sn(3,clutch) sn(4,grC-2) sn(5,brakes) sn(6,mode) sb(1,gb1) sb(2,gb2) sb(3,gb3) sb(4,gb4) sb(5,starter) end
